{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/extras/\u7279\u91cc\u683c\u62c9\u592b\u5927\u62db.gif?t=1738055434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your Mecha Card Game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ACE Strategy is a mecha Card Game where you can pilot various mechas, build your strategies and decks, and engage in battles with pilots across the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/extras/1017\u56de\u5408\u8fc7\u7a0b001.gif?t=1738055434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Various Mechas!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each mecha is designed with an exclusive form and thematic style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Believe in your mecha, and your mecha will respond to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/extras/\u8d5d\u6ce2\u5927\u62db.gif?t=1738055434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique Strategies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are equipment, tactic, and counter cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equipment cards will be attached to your mecha after you use them, and they will have lasting effects, yet tactic and counter cards will affect the battle once and immediately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/extras/\u5341\u5b57\u661f\u53d8\u5f62.gif?t=1738055434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The mecha is the carrier of strength, and the card is the reach of strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make use of your cards and mecha abilities, build your strategy, and fight for your victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/extras/\u730e\u6237\u5ea7\u884c\u661f\u8d2f\u5c04.gif?t=1738055434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u3010Join the Community!\u3011</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel free to join our Discord server to meet with other pilots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Closed beta on PC will be announced soon!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738055434","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/page.bg.jpg?t=1738055434","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/5e50cdb2f6e5977df6b2f54456656c1dee2b75f9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738055434","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/5e50cdb2f6e5977df6b2f54456656c1dee2b75f9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738055434","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127770/extras/\u7279\u91cc\u683c\u62c9\u592b\u5927\u62db.gif?t=1738055434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your Mecha Card Game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ACE Strategy is a mecha Card Game where you can pilot various mechas, build your strategies and decks, and engage in battles with pilots across the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st